'''Jade''' is a type of semi-precious [[gem]]. Jades can be cut from [[uncut jade]]s with level 13 Crafting by using a [[chisel]], granting 20 experience. While cutting jades, the player may accidentally crush an uncut jade into a [[crushed gem]] and will receive only 5 Crafting experience. When used with a [[furnace]] and [[jewellery]] [[mould]], they can be used to make jade jewellery.

