===Cutting chance===
The chance to successfully cut a jade is: <math>\frac{\lfloor(\text{level}-1)*145/98+101\rfloor}{256}</math>{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1084600993038389248|date=13 January 2019|archiveurl=https://archive.fo/HYHsC|archivedate=14 June 2019}}

{{Skilling success chart|label=Gem cutting rates
|label1=Opal|low1=128|high1=250|req1=1|color1=gray|image1=Opal.png
|label2=Jade|low2=100|high2=245|req2=13|color2=green|image2=Jade.png
|label3=Red topaz|low3=90|high3=240|req3=16|color3=pink|image3=Red topaz.png
}}

Based on this probability formula, the price of uncut jade {{Coins|{{GEP|Uncut jade}}}}, and the price of jade {{Coins|{{GEP|Jade}}}}, the minimum crafting level to breakeven or better when flipping jade is {{GemBreakeven
| uncut = {{GEP|Uncut jade}}
| cut = {{GEP|Jade}}
| r = 1.4795918367
| beta = 101
| gamma = 256}}.

